The paper deals with the problem of active object recognition, which involves decision-making and control in robotics (cs.RO) to recognize objects in images (cs.CV) using machine learning techniques such as LSTM networks (cs.AI, cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of Belief Tree Search, which is a technique commonly used in control and decision-making problems (cs.SY).
